name: Trendy Downtown Condo with 2 Beds and Parking (E3)
description:
Beautifully decorated 2 bedroom apartment with secure underground parking in the heart of Downtown Vancouver!
** kitchen was been updated as of October 2019 with new stainless steel appliances and light backsplash. Updated photos coming soon**
This suite comes fully stocked with all essentials that you will need for your stay in Vancouver as well as cable TV, high-speed Wi-Fi, home phone, in suite laundry, dishwasher, portable AC unit and a full gym.

The space
Master Bedroom has a Queen Bed and Junior Bedroom has a Single Bed.

This Home Away From Home is Well Stocked with Towels and Linens, a Fully Equipped Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances and Granite Counter Tops.
Price Includes Cable Television, Local Telephone, Wireless High-Speed Internet, In-Suite Laundry, Dishwasher and Parking. For Your Enjoyment You Will Also Have Access to the Common Room and Gym Facilities!

The apartment is located very close to Robson Stree

name: Hygge House
description:
Cozy and bright ground floor unit designed perfectly to accommodate one or two families. A little bit modern, a little bit bohemian and very flexible in how it is set up, this home is a shapeshifter that can adapt to your needs. Just a few blocks from the lovely and bustling Commercial Drive, Trout Lake Park and Commercial/Broadway station, it's exceptionally convenient yet maintains a calm neighbourhood feel. We love living here, and we think you'll like it too :)

The space
Our home reflects all the things we value in the pursuit of a good life. It's an amazing place to cook and enjoy big communal meals, and to have cozy evening gatherings with lots of friends and family. With its open concept and custom furniture (hand built by us!), it's designed specifically to accommodate many people, yet still feel warm and welcoming. name: Brand New 2 bed room basement
description:
Brand new suite just for you. Access to different places through transit such as Downtown Vancouver, UBC, Langara, YVR airport, Metrotown shopping centre and numerous community centres and tourist attractions.

The space
Brand new basement suite with private access, very quiet and comfortable. We have 1 queen size bed and one full size bed in two bedrooms, also one futon which can transfer to 1 queen size bed in living area.

Guest access
Guests may access the gate and the path at 1968 Nassau Drive in which leads to the spacious, brand new, and comfortable 2 bedroom 1 bathroom basement suite at 1972 Nassau Drive.

Other things to note
We also have included a spacious new kitchen with a Refrigerator, microwave, stove and oven. There is also a washer and dryer in suite.
